cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.NI 

This paper discusses a defense mechanism for cloud containers, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of live migration and behavior monitoring, which are related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE), respectively. The concept of a search game is related to control systems (cs.SY), and the evaluation of the mechanism involves simulation, which is related to networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
